https://github.com/ethicalhack3r/DVWA

1. Download and install as a docker container:
    https://hub.docker.com/r/vulnerables/web-dvwa/
1)docker pull vulnerables/web-dvwa
docker run --rm -it -p 80:80 vulnerables/web-dvwa
2)localhost/setup.php     create/reset database
login:  admin  password
set the difficulty level: the default is impossible level, can change it in DVWA Security 
Attention: ensure you are using aufs due to previous mysql issues, Run docker info to check storage driver

2. Download and Installation
add-apt-repository ppa:ondrej/php
apt-get update
apt-get install php5.6
apt-get install php5.6-mbstring php5.6-mcrypt php5.6-mysql php5.6-xml php5.6-gd
locate etc/php
php -v
systemctl start apache2
(a2dismod php7.0
a2enmod php5.6)
cd /var/www/ && wget https://github.com/ethicalhack3r/DVWA/archive/v1.9.zip
unzip v1.9.zip -d html/
cd html/ && mv DVWA-1.9 dvwa
locate php.ini

vi /etc/php/5.6/apache2/php.ini
allow_url_include=On
vi /var/www/html/dvwa/config/config.inc.php

chgrp www-data /var/www/html/dvwa/hackable/uploads
chgrp www-data /var/www/html/dvwa/external/phpids/0.6/lib/IDS/tmp/phpids_log.txt
chmod g+w uploads
chmod g+w log.txt

http://172.17.0.2/dvwa/index.php
